OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cattempted murder after Edinburgh
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FA 36-year-old man from Edinburgh has
OL,8,Fappeared in court charged with five
OL,9,Fcounts of attempted murder "aggravated
OL,10,Fby reason of having a terrorist
OL,11,Fconnection" after a series of alleged
OL,12,Fanti-Muslim attacks in the city on
OL,13,FFriday.
OL,15,FLewis Hawkes was also charged with one
OL,16,Fcount of assault and robbery, two
OL,17,Fcounts of breach of the peace and two
OL,18,Fcounts of culpable and reckless
OL,19,Fconduct.
