OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782211684
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cattempted murder after Edinburgh
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FThe additional charges were also
OL,8,Faggravated by reason of having a
OL,9,Fterrorist connection, the Crown Office
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FCounter-terrorism officers were
OL,13,Fbrought in to investigate the attacks
OL,14,Facross the city on Friday, which left
OL,15,Ffive people injured and are suspected
OL,16,Fto have an anti-Muslim motivation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
