OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782211684
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cattempted murder after Edinburgh
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,8,Fspoke to some of those who were
OL,9,Finjured in the attacks, saying they
OL,10,Fwere "deeply traumatised" by what
OL,11,Fhappened to them.
OL,13,FSwinney expressed his "deepest
OL,14,Fsympathy" to all those affected by the
OL,15,Fviolence and said he wanted to send a
OL,16,Fmessage of "solidarity and sympathy
OL,17,Fand empathy" to the wider Muslim
OL,18,Fcommunity in Scotland.
