OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782211684
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cattempted murder after Edinburgh
OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FHawkes did not submit a plea during a
OL,8,Fprivate hearing at Edinburgh Sheriff
OL,9,FCourt on Monday.
OL,11,FHe was committed for further
OL,12,Fexamination and remanded in custody,
OL,13,Fahead of another court appearance
OL,14,Fwithin eight days.
